{"tid":735105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土耳其火車出軌至少24死338傷","createTime":"2018-07-09T08:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T08:36:56.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec2b8290ccb454573a08475b7e49c13bc9baf45","tid":735105,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180709/_2018070915030853704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180709%2F_2018070915030853704.jpg&h=6a822e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">火車駛至泰基爾達省時，其中6個車卡出軌。AP<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n土耳其一列載着368人的火車周日出軌，造成至少24人死亡，338人受傷，當中124人仍然留醫。事故疑因連日暴雨導致路軌路基塌陷，釀成脫軌。<br />\n<br />\n事發於西北部接壤希臘和保加利亞的泰基爾達省，當時火車正由埃迪爾內省開往伊斯坦布爾，共載有362名乘客和6名乘務人員。火車駛至泰基爾達省時，其中6個車卡出軌。事發後，大批救援人員和超過100部救護車趕往現場救援。軍方亦派出多架直升機參與救援。<br />\n<br />\n泰基爾達省長傑伊蘭表示，發生事故的原因是暴雨導致鐵路路基塌陷。事發現場因近日大雨而變得滿地泥濘。當地傳媒發放的圖片顯示，有路軌下的土地塌陷。<br />\n<br />\n從現場圖片可見，列車嚴重翻側，部分車廂甚至落在路軌旁的泥地；有救護員即場為傷者包紮，有多人被抬上擔架，亦有乘客能自已步行離開。總統埃爾多安下令全力救人，並向死傷者送上慰問。<br />\n<br />\n一名生還者告訴美國有線電視新聞網土耳其頻道 (CNN Turk)，他在現場看到10具以上罹難者屍體。另一名生還者說：「很多人當場死亡，有人的腳被砸爛，這是很可怕的事故。」<br />\n當局事後以國家安全及公眾秩序為由，向傳媒頒布臨時禁令，禁止傳媒播放現場的慘烈畫面。<br />\n當地傳媒引述衛生部長德米爾詹說，事發後有338人要送院治療，當中124人仍然留醫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180709/_2018070915030823370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180709%2F_2018070915030823370.jpg&h=f7da04e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180709/_2018070915031099532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180709%2F_2018070915031099532.jpg&h=b13cec4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/761038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F761038&d=GJRuu0le9nCCcQ5n9mq0y8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=8fb84264\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F761038&h=f6d2d174\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/761038</a><br />\n<br />\n最近咁多災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce49ae1b1903873f240d928c500a847874db4d30","tid":735105,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:22:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾回教徒"},{"pid":"4a329da4a14e0ddd9cd335148395264e3e04500b","tid":735105,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"中國制造?"},{"pid":"a8cdd474966837e99da2cf9d5a8042d9307ee4e8","tid":735105,"uid":192263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4992b0917a6f443e89919c4f8b9bf71a77166a1f","tid":735105,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"a74fe61d84123bf392200753ff9d94bd5462c680","tid":735105,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"支式火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}